hvg <- modelGeneVar(sce)
topHvg <- getTopHVGs(hvg, n = 1000)
rowSubset(sce) <- topHvg

set.seed(123)
sce <- fixedPCA(sce, subset.row = topHvg) 
sce <- runTSNE(sce, dimred = "PCA")

plotReducedDim(sce, "TSNE", colour_by = "type")

plotReducedDim(sce, "TSNE", colour_by = "Donor")

plotReducedDim(sce, "TSNE", colour_by = "clusters")
